      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        130.97,
        114.38,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0010",
      "text": "Global Process Logout:",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        130.97,
        235.14,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0011",
      "text": " The Global Process Logout bit shall be set to one, and specifies:",
      "bbox": [
        235.14,
        130.97,
        522.88,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0012",
      "text": "A) only the TYPE code and TYPE code extension fields shall have meaning, along with the",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        154.96,
        539.95,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0013",
      "text": "Global Process Logout bit itself;",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        166.96,
        278.49,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0014",
      "text": "B) all image pairs for all Nx_Ports with which Process Login has been performed shall be re-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        190.96,
        539.97,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0015",
      "text": "moved from the recipient Nx_Port for the specified TYPE; and",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        202.96,
        411.24,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0016",
      "text": "C) all resources associated with the establishment of all image pairs of the specified TYPE at",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        226.96,
        540.06,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p113_s0017",
      "text": "the recipient Nx_Port shall be released.",
      "bbox": [
        138.0,
        238.96,
        312.37,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
